Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玄黄端现 太极混沌如鸡蛋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln the beginning, there was darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.04,0:00:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着轰的一声\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, bang...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生了无限膨胀的时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence...of time, space, and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 所见超乎我们的想像\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, see further than we've ever imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.26,0:00:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越了客观认知极限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beyond the limits of our existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a place we call "The Universe".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科技所提出的承诺\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt promises to deliver technologies...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们的旅行将更遥远 更快捷\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that will carry us everfarther and everfaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而始终充满着致命的危险\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But it's fraught with constant and lethal peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外太空飞行宛如穿行射击场\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Flying in outer space is like going through a shooting gallery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将考验人类的能力与智慧的极限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt will test the limits of human capacity and human ingenuity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果出错了 你将怎么办？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf something goes wrong, what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无能为力 只好坐以待毙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nothing. You just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到太空旅行时代\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Welcome to the age of space travel.
