Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[历史频道] 第二季 第八集 太空旅行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}[History Channel] The UniverseⅡ 08of19 Space.Travel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以几乎不曾想过的方式 以平稳的上进之手\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln ways scarcely even imagined, the steady hand of progress...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平稳地将人类送上天空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is poised to deliver humanity to the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少年来 神秘辉煌的宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For ages, the mysterious splendor of the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.54,0:01:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从其遥远的高处引诱着我们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}has enticed us from its remote heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于 其神秘的诱惑已触手可及了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}At last, its mysterious temptations are within reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类的命运可以实现了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and man's destiny can be fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道我们基因里的命令\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l don't know if it's writ in our genes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一旦你看到远处的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but anytime you see something at a distance...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它激起了你的好奇心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it piques your curiosity...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.98,0:01:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你立马想要做的事就是凑近看看\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the first thing you want to do is get a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 望远镜在这一点上让你看得够远了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, while telescopes get you pretty far in this regard...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些东西已经近到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}those things that are sort of close enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的太空计划已触手可及了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to be within the reach of our space program...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时 为何不去旅行一番呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}why not take the trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒计时十 九…\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}T-minus ten, nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主发动机点火\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}main engine start.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五 四 亚特兰大号升空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Five, four, and lift-off of Space Shuttle "Atlantis".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.37,0:02:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窥视摆脱地球的控制\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Prying free from our home planet's grip...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跻身人类最伟大的成就\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ranks among the greatest of human achievements.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 1972年以来 尚无人大胆超越地球的轨道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But no one since 1972 has ventured beyond the Earth's orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的太空计划已经卡住了30年了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our space program has been stuck for thirty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是围绕着地球转\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We simply just go around the planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就像哥伦布首次发现新大陆后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's just like Columbus exploring the New world for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,余生就消磨在西班牙海岸边游荡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then spending the rest of his life..simply puttering around the Spanish coastline.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题出在哪里？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出在肮脏的两个字上 "开销"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's a dirty little four-letterword...and that is "cost".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将一磅东西送入轨道的成本约1万美元\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt costs about $10,000 to put a pound of anything into orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到约翰·格列(宇航员)是纯金打造的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lmagine John Glenn made out of solid gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是将约翰·格列或你送入轨道的代价\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's what it costs to put John Glenn or you into orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将花费2000万美元\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt would cost about $20 million...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你送去太空站作周末游\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for you to take a weekend trip up to the Space Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将花费5亿美元把你送上月球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt would cost about a half a billion dollars...for you to go to the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你要去火星的话\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And for you to go to Mars...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许要花上数百亿美元才行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would probably cost tens of billions of dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缩减太空旅行开支的方法之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One way to reduce the cost of reaching space...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是找到克服地球引力更有效的办法\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would be to find a more efficient way to overcome Earth's gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得《杰克与魔豆》的故事吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Remember the story of Jack and the Beanstalk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰克就是那个攀爬着魔豆上天的小男孩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Jack was a little boy who climbed the beanstalk into heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 想像一下有一架太空电梯 你按一下按钮"上"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Well, imagine a space elevator such that you hit the "up" button...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电梯就带你上天\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the elevator takes you into the heavens...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像杰克与魔豆那样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just like Jack and the Beanstalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是从下往上建造\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lnstead of building from the ground up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太空电梯是自上而下建造的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the space elevatorwould be built from the top down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同步轨道卫星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A satellite in geosynchronous orbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:04:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下一根6万英里的缆绳到地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would drop a 60,000-mile cable back to Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它将被锚固在地面上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where it would be anchored to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们已经接近于有能力创造出纤维\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now we are within striking distance of being able to create fibers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来承受太空电梯在地球轨道上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that can with stand the tension...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以超高速上下移动所产生的张力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of traveling at enormous velocities in outer space...as the space elevator rotates with the planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它永远不会掉下来是因为它的运转速度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So it never falls because it rotates...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等同于地球的速度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at the same rate as the planet Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电梯的轿厢沿着缆绳盘旋而上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The elevator's compartment would simply roll up the cable...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将乘客和补给送上轨道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}shuttling travelers and supplies into orbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里等候飞船\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where it would wait for a spacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一系统将完全取代传统的火箭发射\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This system would entirely replace a conventional rocket launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有可能减少太空旅行的开销1000倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And that might reduce the cost of space travel...by a factor of a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试想一下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着你开始意识到或许外太空之旅\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Then you begin to realize that perhaps a trip to outer space...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能不比飞机票差多少\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}may be no worse than an airplane ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 超越了地球亲切拥抱的界限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But beyond the limits of Earth's comforting embrace...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外部的威胁在等待着每一位太空游客\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}exotic menaces await every space traveler.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞行在外太空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Flying in outer space...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不像在陆地上开车畅游了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is not like taking a nice ride in the country in a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是穿行在射击场里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's like going through a shooting gallery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于一个不知情的游客来说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To an unsuspecting voyager...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就似乎是宇宙在举枪瞄准一样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it might seem the universe is taking aim with a firearm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太空中存在着粒子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There are particles in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至灰尘大小的颗粒 如卵石大小的颗粒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}even dust-sized particles, pebble-sized particles...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其时速达到了数万英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that are traveling tens of thousands of miles an hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时甚至更快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and sometimes even faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,50多万的弹丸直径超过了一英吋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}More than half a million of these projectiles...measuring over an inch in diameter...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正在我们地球周围呼啸而过\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are zipping around our planet right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中包括太阳能电池的玻璃碎片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They include pieces of glass broken off of solar cells...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航天器的装饰碎片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}paint chips from spacecraft...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及火箭助推器的碎片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and debris from rocket booster engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了深太空会有更大的危险\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And in deeper space, there's more danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:06:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自卵石般大小的流星叫做微流星体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from pebble-sized meteors called micrometeoroids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一小粒尘埃可以击碎玻璃 洞穿金属\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A small piece of dust can crack glass, it can penetrate metal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以粉碎塑料\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it can pulverize plastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是太空中始终出现的情况\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And that does happen in space all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许还有更致命的危险\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But perhaps an even more deadly danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:20.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不是固体 潜伏在那里:辐射\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}not at all solid, lies in wait: Radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个无形能量的破坏力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The devastating effects of this invisible energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经在地球上目睹过\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}have been witnessed on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二战期间的原子弹的后果\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the aftermath of the atomic bombs of world War ll...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切尔诺贝利的核尘埃\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the nuclearfallout of Chernobyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人不安的是维持我们生命的太阳\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Distressingly, our own life-giving Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在喷发出有害的辐射\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}spews out streams of poisonous radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此要意识到我们一直得到这个摇篮的呵护\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So realize that we've been protected in this cradle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们受到了地球大气层的保护\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We've been protected by the atmosphere of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球磁场吞噬了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The magnetic field of the Earth gobbles up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳发出的耀斑并创造了北极光\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}most of the flares from the Sun to create the Aurora Borealis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在太空里你可以看到北极光迎面而来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln outer space, you get the Aurora Borealis coming right at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有臭氧层\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's no ozone layer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有磁场来保护你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there's no magnetic field to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你和外太空的恶劣环境\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's just you and the harshness of outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们地球与太阳的距离\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}At our home planet's distance from the Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大约9000万英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}roughly ninety million miles away...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球的周围每秒钟每平方英吋的太空中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}several hundred million solar particles...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有几亿个太阳粒子穿过\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}pass through each square inch of space...every second around our Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都是太阳一刻不停流出的高能粒子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's high-energy particles streaming from the Sun all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而有时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But every now and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有一次这些粒子的超大剂量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there's an extra dose of these particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳打嗝吐出高能辐射\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Sun burps up high-energy radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's bad, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种辐射水平对人的DNA没什么好处\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That level of radiation it is never good for one's DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳黑子爆发出这些超量的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sunspots flare up these extra doses of energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像宇宙大炮的连续轰击\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like a battery of cannons bombarding the cosmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在其抵达前根本无法获知其行径\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's no way to know that they're going to be here...before they arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不幸的是 还是存在着辐射的危险\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Unfortunately, there's still a risk of radiation...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管我们远离了太阳\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}even as we get farther from the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为还有一个危险的能量潜伏着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's because another invading energy lurks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的银河宇宙射线\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Known as galactic cosmic rays...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们来自遥远的外部世界的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they hail from the distant alien worlds...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恒星爆炸和黑洞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of exploding stars and black holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河宇宙射线是以近乎光速穿行的粒子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Galactic cosmic rays are particles that are traveling at speeds...very close to the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是一个铁粒子撞进你的身体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Even a single particle of iron slamming into your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会具有职业棒球的效果\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}can have the effect of a Major League baseball...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时速上百英里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}at a hundred miles an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具有毁灭性\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They can be devastating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管沉重的铁粒子相当罕见\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Although heavy iron particles are rare...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:09:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是置身航天器保护之外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}outside of the protection of a spacecraft...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸如宇航员在舱外漫步时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}such as when an astronaut performs a spacewalk...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每秒钟会有数以千计的银河宇宙射线\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}thousands of galactic cosmic rays...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过你的身体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}do penetrate the body every second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每昼夜银河宇宙射线和太阳粒子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Every 24 hours, the galactic cosmic rays and solar particles...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击太空游客带来的辐射\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}attack a space traveler with as much radiation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当于地球居民六个月里所接受的量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as a surface dweller on Earth receives in six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人体不会马上感觉到辐射的影响\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The human body won't immediately feel the impacting radiation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是到了一定的量就可以觉察到了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but in sufficient quantities, it can be noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使闭上眼睛 粒子也会金星闪烁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Even with eyes closed, the particles spark flashes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此时它们在轰击太空游客的视网膜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when they strike a space traveler's retina.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪烁不会致盲 但你不得不问自己\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The flashes are not blinding, and you have to ask yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我都看到了什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}"Hmm, did l see something"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你会说:"噢 看到了"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And then you say, "Oh, yes, l did".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.46,0:09:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后其模样时不时有所差异\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And then its appearances are a little different from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.01,0:09:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样 人体确实感觉到了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}However, the human body does feel the shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种奇特的失重经历的震惊\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of this bizarre weightless existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为进入太空最危险的情况\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}l think that the most dangerous thing going into space...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是失重\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is the loss of gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失重会引起你身体几乎每个系统都\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Weightlessness causes almost every system in your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始变化 变化不会停止\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to start changing, and it doesn't stop changing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你再次回到有重力的世界\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}until you get back onto a world...where you're pulled down again by its gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零重力的第一批受害者之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One of the first casualties of zero gravity...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是太空游客的方向感\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is a space traveler's sense of direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上下方向在哪？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What's up and what's down?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好的问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Very good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样 这是你首先要弄明白的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And first of all, it's whatever you want it to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你认为这是上 那非常好\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf you want this to be up, that's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你认为这是上 那还算过的去\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but If you want this to be up, that's just as good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多数游客会患上晕动病\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Most travelers will suffer from motion sickness...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在开头的几个小时甚者几天\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for the first few hours or, most likely, days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是避免不了的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's just one of those things...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只得听天由命\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that you ought to resign yourself to facing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:11:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都极有可能感觉到方向感有一点混乱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that everyone is very likely to feel a little bit disturbed...in terms of orientation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球上水肺潜水员飘浮在水下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Here on Earth, scuba divers floating underwater...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.83,0:11:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体验到长时间无重力最接近的感受\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}experience the nearest sensation of prolonged periods without gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是出于这个原因有志成为宇航员的人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt is for this very reason that aspiring NASA astronauts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在无重力的环境中训练生活和工作\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}train to live and work in a gravity-free environment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过将他们自己一次六个小时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by subjecting themselves for up to six hours at a time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放在一个大水罐里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a large water tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在水下呼吸器 你还是能感受到重力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, scuba equipment, you still experience the forces of gravity...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是它感觉不出来 因为你整个身子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but it doesn't feel like it because your whole body...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被水均匀地托起 将你浮起来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is uniformly buoyed by the water that holds you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了可以看到表面漂起的水泡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And except for the visual cue of air bubbles floating to the surface...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在水下游泳可以模拟失去方向的感觉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}swimming underwater can mimic the sensation of disorientation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是随着时间的流逝在失重的太空中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But, as time passes in the weightlessness of space...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人体感觉到已无需抵抗重力了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the human body senses it no longer needs to resist the force of gravity...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肌肉骨质就开始流失了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and begins shedding muscle and bone mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身处太空中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When you're in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身体会认为你可能还在床上睡觉呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}your body thinks you might as well be lying in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:10.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要是你不加留意的话你的身体就会萎缩\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And so If you're not careful, your body will atrophy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了抗衡此作用每天在太空中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To counter this, each day in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇航员都必须进行锻炼\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}an astronaut needs to exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很少使用腿 所以腿特别容易受伤\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The legs are especially vulnerable because they are seldom used.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个天地里双臂双手在搬动身体中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln this world, the arms and hands do most of the work...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳动强度最大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to move the body around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.29,0:12:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常要碰到的最困难的事情\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What would be the toughest thing to get used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可能就是你生活在太空中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}might very well be just how you live in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能在房间里走动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where you can't walk across the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须漂移到你要去的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You have to float everywhere you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失重也会减缓消化功能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The lack of gravity also slows down the digestive tract...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:52.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就会引起进餐的问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which can cause problems at mealtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的消化系统会停摆\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Your digestive system stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能吃 不能喝\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can't eat, you can't drink...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到你重新开始消化为止\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}until you can start digesting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那无论如何都可能会耽误上几个小时到几天工夫\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And that can take anywhere from hours to days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更为糟糕的是失重与辐射会以\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Worse still, zero gravity and radiation can combine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个特别危险的方式结合在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in an especially sinisterway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太空中免疫系统不会如平常那个那样有效\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln space, the immune system is not as effective as it normally is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:23.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们平常能够承受的许多细菌和病毒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And many of the bacteria and viruses...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得愈加危险\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that we normally can withstand become more virulent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上细菌的繁殖可能会快上50倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Additionally, bacteria can grow up to fifty times faster...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上去的病毒 可能会变异成前所未有的杀手\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and any virus brought onboard...could mutate into a never-before-seen predator...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祸根在于无处不在的辐射\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}thanks to the ever-present radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有这些困难折磨着太空游客\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All these difficulties prey on space travelers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最先的几个小时乃至几天里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in just the first few hours or days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长时间的旅游又如何呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And what aboutjourneys that need more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会变得愈加艰难\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt only gets tougher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙是个无情的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The universe is an unforgiving place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它只开放给最大胆的冒险家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's open to only the boldest adventurers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们具有勇往直前的勇气\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}those who have the mettle to trek deep...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深入充满危险的环境之中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}into an environment swimming with toxic hazards...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不畏艰险远离安全熟悉的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and unafraid to stray far from the safe and familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们视为理所当然的 穿着轻便\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We take it for granted that clothing is flexible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在室温中作业\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and machines work in room temperature...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为或明或暗 本来就应该这样的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because, implicitly or explicitly, they're designed for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你进入了深太空 要是你面对太阳\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You go into the depths of space, If you're facing the Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温度就可能达到数百华氏度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it could be hundreds of degrees Fahrenheit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你背离太阳\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf you're facing away from the Sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可能是零下几百度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it could be hundreds of degrees below zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球上有很多你都视为理所当然的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Down here on Earth, you take so much for granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我们在户外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You know, we're out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阳光 新鲜空气都包围着你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the sunshine, the fresh air all around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里你就处在一个封闭的生态系统里了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Up there, you're in a closed ecosystem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须提供所有的人类必需品\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You have to supply all the human needs...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:15:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球上 会自动照应我们的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that the Earth just, you know, automatically does for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不得不指望 整个船停靠在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You have to hope that the integrity of the hull...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就不会快速减压 很快窒息\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}stays together so you don't have rapid decompression...quick suffocation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的现实也存在于在海洋深处游荡的潜艇\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The same reality exists for a submarine...liding deep through the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它提供了一个生命保护屏障来保护其居民\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt provides a life-preserving barrier to protect its inhabitants...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免受周围的外部世界的威胁\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from a surrounding alien world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如飞船损坏 空气就会泄漏 你就会玩儿完\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf there's damage to the spaceship, air leaks out, you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜艇损坏 水会进入 你也会玩儿完\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Damage to submarine, water gets in, you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 孤独 生理和个人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So the isolation, both physically and personally...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两者之间似乎相当类似\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}between the two seems quite parallel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜在的灾难性事故潜伏着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The potential for a catastrophic mishap lurks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你身处海洋深处\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When you're out in the middle of the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只有自己和同伴可以依靠\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you have only yourself and your colleagues to rely on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太空中的情况也是一样的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the same thing applies in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都必须承受得住\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Things have to hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可能回家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可能跑去五金商店\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can't run to the hardware store.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可能用某些没带来的部件来修理东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can't fix the thing with some part that you didn't bring along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只能利用人类智慧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And you're stuck with human ingenuity...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这你随身携带的工具\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the tools you brought with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了外太空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And out there in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的远离了人类\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you truly are just removed from mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种孤独是我以前从未体会过的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt is isolation like l've neverfelt before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升空 我们已经升空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Lift off, we have lift off...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通常我们探索太空的努力一直比喻为\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Often our efforts to explore space have been analogized...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,15 16世纪的伟大的探险家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to the great explorers of the 15th and 16th century...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首次越洋发现新大陆\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the first to cross the oceans, going to unknown territory...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上所有的补给\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}having to bring all their supplies with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道他们是否还会回来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}not knowing if they'll ever return.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想对那种比喻有很多话要说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And l think there's a lot to say about that analogy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 有一点是不堪一击的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But there's a point where it breaks down badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会号登陆南美时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When Cortes landed in South America...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥伦布抵达加勒比时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when Columbus hit the Caribbean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是还有空气让他呼吸吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}there was still air there for him to breathe, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树上长着水果\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There was fruit on the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设想一下阿波罗11号宇航员 阿姆斯特朗和奥尔德林\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Suppose the Apollo 11 astronauts, Neil Armstrong and BuzzAldrin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登陆月球 比如发动机坏了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}landed on the Moon and, like, the engine broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 休斯顿 我们现在出现了问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Okay, Houston, we've had a problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,束手无策 只是等死\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nothing. You just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.24,0:17:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那种发动机树\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's not sort of an engine tree...
